divs: Sighting DetailsI was on the phone with a friend on my dock in the back yard and was watching the sky,I thought I saw something moving very slow over the water facing the West of the Gulf of Mexico. I blink my eyes to take a better look, and blink again then WOW all of a sudden there was this Very large object with around 10 steady lights. With 4 missing lights to make a perfect circle. It was moving very fast to the south. I ran in to get my husband but when we ran out it was gone. I was so shook up I couldn't even talk or catch my breath. I had goose bumps and all my body for a hour. Its was the most exciting thing I have ever seen in my life. I can't tell you it was a UFO of anything else. I will say it was something I have NEVER seen before in the sky. I still can't get it out of my head. I hope that if I ever get a chance to see something like that again, I will beable to keep myself together better. What a wonderful thing to see. I hope that someone else in my area also got to see it. Thank you for your time. Brenda Markle
Summary: I saw a 3/4 Circle moving very low over the canal on my dock moving to the south
